 a length. Charlie Bennett sticks,  and while this is a deeper field, her current form demands serious respect. 4. YASSA broke his maiden over this trip here last start, showing good improvement and suggesting there’s more to come. He is lightly raced, progressive, and with Pinheiro staying aboard, he is a definite top 4 contender. 1. RB AL QAAHER continues to hold strong Group-level form, placing again over 1800m in G3 company at Meydan last start. He is ultra consistent, has a great association with Saif Al Balushi, and he should measure up once more. 10. MONTECRISTO brings winning dirt form from Al Ain, including a last-start 2000m victory. This is tougher, but he’s in good shape and cannot be dismissed. Include in all combinations.\",\"runners\":[12,4,1,10],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Racing  and Sports","tipRunnerNumbers":[12,4,1]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,4,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,12,3,2]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,12,1,4]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,4,1,9]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,4,3,14]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,2,1,3]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,1,3,4]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"w